}

# =============================================
# NOTES:
# =============================================
# 1. SSL certificates are automatically obtained from Let's Encrypt
# 2. Certificates auto-renew before expiration
# 3. HTTP traffic automatically redirects to HTTPS
# 4. All backend services stay private on Mac Mini
# 5. Only Njalla VPS is publicly accessible
# 6. Tailscale provides encrypted tunnel to Mac Mini
# 7. Update {{ mac_mini_tailscale_ip }} with actual Tailscale IP
#
# Security Best Practices:
# - Mac Mini has NO public ports open
# - Only Tailscale VPN can reach Mac Mini
# - Caddy handles SSL termination
# - Security headers on all responses
# - Rate limiting available (uncomment if needed)
# - Basic auth available for sensitive services
# =============================================
